** CEPHALOTRON 2 **
        by
  Pete W Storonskij

** OFFICIAL DESCRIPTION OF CEPHALOTRON 2 **

CephaloTron 2 is Pete W Storonskij's combined Tron-Artillery game.  You play Light Cycles, but with ultimate weapons!  It has the WeaponForge stacking system that lets you stack up to 12 warheads in one Torpedeux.  You can construct your Torpedeux exactly to your taste with 380 warheads of 50 types to choose from.  This makes for an infinite combination of ultimately overpowered weapon designs.  All 30 players have 5 of their own custom weapons and automatic shields, as well as 3 gears to shift into during play.  You can make Lava Storms, Airstrikes, and Centillions upon Centillions of other weaons.

