Stratoplex: 3D Tron is my previous release, and also (temporarily) my flagship video game for my games armada.  It's on Aminet NOW, in game/2play!

Stratoplex has 3D LightCycles, 3D MCP Cone, 3D Mazes, 3D Asteroids, Strategema, Weapon Modulation, and Shield Configuration sequences.  Tornadeux Drones, Lightning, Thunder, and Fog augment the 3D first person landscape view, letting you experience liquid velocity first hand.

